headline: Hershey Completes Acquisition of LesserEvil, Expanding Consumer Choice
summary: The Hershey Company has closed its acquisition of LesserEvil, the maker of organic, delectable snacks that combine bold flavors with better-for-you ingredients. This acquisition expands the variety of snacking choices Hershey can offer consumers, adding a high-growth brand that complements the company's existing portfolio and brings additional manufacturing capacity.

headline: Hershey closes LesserEvil acquisition as it looks to ‘lead the future of snacking’
summary: The purchase of the better-for-you puffs and popcorn maker comes as the confectionery giant aims to grow its salty snacks division to 20% of revenue during the next decade.
